                  </persName>
            , the Landlord at the Magpye and Horshoe, deposed to the searching of them, and produced 8 handkerchiefs in court, taken upon Smith, one of which the Prosecutor swore to as his Property.</p>
               <p>Hutton called his father and two other men, who spoke well as to his character</p>
